Package org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.database.road

Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.database.road.Node
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TrafficLightNode
    public class Node
extends Object
    This represents a node in the network graph. It basically is the same as an OSM node with a few additions for easy access to dependant information.
